text: ( Source : Sinn Féin ) 13 October , 2015 - by Liadh Ní Riada MEP Sinn Féin MEP Liadh Ní Riada will host a major fisheries policy conference in Dungarvan on Saturday, October 24th . The conference will bring together fishermen, fisheries experts
